channel.title: Looking For A Dev Team For A New Project
channel.description: Hello. I am currently starting a new rsps project, and I would like to get a development team started. I am not giving up on this project, whether I code it alone or with a group of people. This project may or may not be released, I am mainly doing it for fun, to learn more about coding, and to make friends. If you would like to join the development team, please add me on Skype, and let me know you'd like to join. Skype: rambobarnes Thank you and have a great day!
